snippet.title: Knight Club Official Release Trailer
snippet.description:
KNIGHT CLUB Is a 2-4 player action platform-fighting game THAT Brings traditional fighting game elements into an unlocked, free form movement playstyle. Equip your favorite armaments and do battle against your friends locally or online!

Join our community discord over at http://www.gutterarcade.com

Follow Gutter Arcade on twitter http://www.twitter.com/gutterarcade

Trailer by http://www.twitter.com/actionCancel
